    <innerclass refid="classleash_21" prot="public">leash/1</innerclass>
    <briefdescription>
<para>The following predicates are available to control the debugging of programs: </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>debug</para>
<para>Switches the debugger on</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>debugging</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><verbatim>Outputs status information about the debugger which includes the leash
</verbatim> mode and the existing spy-points, when the debugger is on</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>nodebug</para>
<para>Switches the debugger off</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
